These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, daffodil, marigold, rose, zinnia, amaryllis
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, indian, italian, french, turkish, russian, thai
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, november, january, september, june, may, april
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate, 7up, juice, tea, almond-milk
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the turkish is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
10. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
11. the russian is the person who growsdaffodil##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
13. the turkish is on the right of the indian##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
15. the person who growsdaffodil is between the canadian and the person drinking juice##2
16. the russian is on the left of the italian##1
17. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking juice##1
18. the french is on the far left or far right##3
19. the russian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
20. the russian is the person who growsdaffodil##1
21. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
22. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
23. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the canadian##3
24. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
25. the turkish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
26. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |       3        |       4       |     5      |     6      |      7       |
| Flower        | poppy | zinnia     | daffodil           | marigold          | rose  | amaryllis | daisy         |
| Nationality         | thai  | canadian | russian | italian   | indian | turkish   | french       |
